text: Elle () is a 2016 French German Belgian thriller movie directed by Paul Verhoeven and was based on the novel Oh... by Philippe Dijan. It stars Isabelle Huppert (in her Oscar nominated role), Laurent Lafitte, Anne Consigny, Christian Berkel, Virginie Efira, Charles Berling, Alice Isaaz, Judith Magre, Lucas Prisor, Vimala Pons, Jonas Bloquet. ==Other websites== * Category:2016 thriller movies Category:French thriller movies Category:German thriller movies Category:Belgian thriller movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Paul Verhoeven
title: Elle (movie)
